race.comment: HEART 'N' POWER (11) is another strong winning chance for the sharp Clinton Taylor barn. Won her Maiden at Rockhampton by a space and then delivered this track/trip in a 55. Has the speed to clear the awkward gate and she is well placed to go on with the job. KOBAYASTAR (8) peaks and has been within range here her last three. Finally draws an inside barrier and Wiggins is a key jockey switch. Peaks today and can form the quinella. UNIFIES (4) is a former Victorian who will be better for his two runs back following a yard switch. Led and won his Maiden at Sale in August and that form would have him right in the finish. LET'S RIDE (12) will be much more competitive back to a sprint and keep her onside.
